---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Contact — Wychwood Partners" description="Book a call to pressure-test execution discipline.">
  <main class="shell py-14">
    <h1>Book an Intro Call</h1>

    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
      If you’re a founder, investor, or board member dealing with margin drift, weak cash visibility, stalled integration, or growth that feels less controlled than it should — get in touch.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
      Book a call if you’re ready to talk. Send an email if you have a specific question first. Either way, if there’s a fit I’ll say so — and if there isn’t, I’ll say that too.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">

      <div class="card p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Book a call</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
          If you're ready to talk, you can schedule a short introductory call directly. No preamble required.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://calendar.app.google/RRKFf2z6rNDrmzFE8"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="mt-4 inline-flex rounded-[var(--radius-lg)] bg-[rgb(var(--brand-anchor))] px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white transition hover:opacity-95"
        >
          Book an intro call
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Send a question</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
          Not ready for a call yet? Email a question about your situation and I'll reply directly. No forms, no sequence.
        </p>
        <a
          href="mailto:hello@wychwood-partners.com"
          class="mt-4 inline-flex rounded-[var(--radius-lg)] border border-[rgb(var(--border))] px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-[rgb(var(--text))] transition hover:bg-[rgb(var(--surface-elevated))]"
        >
          hello@wychwood-partners.com
        </a>
        <div class="mt-4">
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/seanfoy/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))] hover:text-[rgb(var(--text))] hover:underline"
          >
            Or connect on LinkedIn →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
    <p class="mt-12 max-w-3xl text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
      Experience across venture-backed growth, private equity hold periods, multi-country scale, and IPO environments.
    </p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
